              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Dans le secteur du BTP, le maître d'ouvrage doit informer les salariés détachés de leurs droits en"
                },
                {
                  "type": "element",
                  "name": "MiseEnEvidence",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " affichant "
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "element",
                  "name": "MiseEnEvidence",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "element",
                      "name": "MiseEnEvidence",
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "da"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "ns le vestiaire"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " les informations concernant :"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "element",
              "name": "Liste",
              "attributes": {
                "type": "puce"
              },
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "element",
                  "name": "Item",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "element",
                      "name": "Paragraphe",
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "la durée du travail,"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "element",
                  "name": "Item",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "element",
                      "name": "Paragraphe",
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "le salaire minimum,"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "element",
                  "name": "Item",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "element",
                      "name": "Paragraphe",
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "l'hébergement,"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "element",
                  "name": "Item",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "element",
                      "name": "Paragraphe",
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "la prévention des chutes de hauteur,"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "element",
                  "name": "Item",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "element",
                      "name": "Paragraphe",
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "les équipements individuels obligatoires,"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "element",
                  "name": "Item",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "element",
                      "name": "Paragraphe",
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "l'existence d'un droit de retrait."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "element",
              "name": "Paragraphe",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "L'affiche précise aussi comment le salarié peut faire valoir ses droits."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "element",
              "name": "Paragraphe",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "L'affiche, obligatoirement réalisée dans l'une des langues officielles de chaque État d'appartenance des salariés détachés, doit rester lisible."
